  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Who Will Remain Standing!? Omni-Leo V.S. Terror Terius!? Find Out on the Last Episode of DNA 1!</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972780/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.poster.avif?t=1755720072\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972780/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.webm?t=1755720072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972780/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.mp4?t=1755720072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play the final episode of DNA 1 where you play as Omni-Leo in the epic finale showdown against Terror Terius, the symbol of darkness...who will remain standing?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972780/extras/5c605fcd5947482ce4dd94e0ff8d5544.avif?t=1755720072\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>At Last the True Power of Leo's DNA Has Awoken!</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Finish DNA 1's epic finale in an ultimate boss battle unlike any you have ever played before...<br><br></li><li>Find out who will remain in the grand showdown between Omni-Leo and Terror Terius.<br><br></li><li> Clash with darkness and discover the fate of the world...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972780/extras/02eb923c6015aa992484d245e4151faf.avif?t=1755720072\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rise Leo...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Finish off DNA 1 with the finale's enticing gameplay!<br><br></li><li>Experience the ultimate challenge building upon all of DNA 1's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Discover the true power within Leo...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972780/extras/5fcdfd174dc7aa66a4ad3fb2920e8226.avif?t=1755720072\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle the Epic Final Showdown in the Cosmos!</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>End DNA 1 in a gripping, remarkable finale beyond the Earth!<br><br></li><li> Take the final fight to the cosmos and find out who shall remain standing in the end!<br><br></li><li> So, who will remain standing...? </li></ul></i>",
